rnal_link.gif" height="12" width="12" style="border:none;"></a>.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/CuteBruiser" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/CuteBruiser">Cute Bruiser</a>: She's short, childish, but incredibly strong and wields a giant battleax as her CHARM.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GirlishPigtails" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GirlishPigtails">Girlish Pigtails</a>: She has long, elegant twin-tails that reach down to her thighs with white ribbons to emphasize her childishness and her (presumed) innocence.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/HappilyEverAfter" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/HappilyEverAfter">Happily Ever After</a>: Although not married, she and Moyu take a Schutzengel Pledge at the credits sequence, which almost looks like a wedding ceremony.</li></ul><p></p></div><p></p><div class="folderlabel" onclick="togglefolder('folder6');">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Kuo Shenlin&nbsp;</div><div id="folder6" class="folder" isfolder="true" style="display:block;"><div class="quoteright" style="width:350px;"><img src="https://static.tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pub/images/kuo_shenlin_6.png" class="embeddedimage" border="0" alt="https://static.tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pub/images/kuo_shenlin_6.png"></div><div class="indent"><strong>Age:</strong> 15 <br><strong>Birthday:</strong> February 6 <br><strong><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/PersonalityBloodTypes" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/PersonalityBloodTypes">Blood type</a>:</strong> A <br><strong>Skills/Interests:</strong> Baths, kungfu tea ceremony, reading about tactics <br><strong>Favorite food:</strong> Pasta, cuisine from her homeland, meat dishes <br><strong><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/WeaponOfChoice" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/WeaponOfChoice">CHARM</a>:</strong> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Characters/ChineseMythology" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Characters/ChineseMythology">Mazu<